    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK432">
<l>ivaṟalu māṇpiṟanta māṉamu māṇā</l>
<l>vuvakaiyu mēta miṟaikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Avarice, undignified pride, and low pleasures are faults in a king.</l>
